SUMMARY:Stardust and Spotlights
DESCRIPTION:Musical theatre includes many genres within it\, such as classical singing\, pop/rock\, jazz\, folk music\, and contemporary music\, and it has evolved over the years. The programme will include songs from the golden age of musical theatre with classic tunes from The Sound of Music\, The King and I\, and Carousel to current musical theatre with catchy tunes from Hamilton\, Mean Girls\, Frozen\, and Wicked. Aleyna Mohanraj has sung on the West End in London in various concerts and pantomimes\, one of the highest levels of performance in musical theatre. \nSupported by: \n \n    Contact        \n  \n
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/stardust-and-spotlights/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Music,Performing Arts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Thumbnail_SS.jpg
END:VEVENT
